da: Skoven er et farligt sted... Da vi var små, fortalte min søster mig nogle gange ting om det.
For eksempel, dyrelivet virker meget sødt i starten, men er faktisk ret farligt!
Jeg aner dog ikke, hvordan hun vidste det... Måske studerede hun omverdenen, og jeg lagde bare aldrig mærke til det?
en: The forest is a dangerous place... When we were little, my sister sometimes told me things about it.
Things like its wildlife seeming very cute at first, but actually being quite dangerous!
I have no idea how she knew, though... Maybe she was studying the outside world and I just never noticed?
